继去年该乐队凭借首张 EDM 专辑登上澳大利亚舞曲排行榜冠军之后</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-and-orville-peck-are-set-to-appear-on-the-wiggles-new-country-album-3828033">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 和奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck) 将出现在 The Wiggles 的新乡村专辑中，</a>该专辑首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dolly-Parton-Anthony-Field-of-The-Wiggles-and-Orville-Peck.-CREDIT_-Terry-Wyatt_WireImage-Matt-Jelonek_WireImage-and-Gary-Miller_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/orville-peck">奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck)</a>将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wiggles">The Wiggles</a>即将发行的乡村专辑中亮相。请在下面找到更多详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-wiggles-rewiggled-review-stella-donnelly-spacey-jane-the-chats-covers-3180407">The Wiggles – “ReWiggled”评论：斯特拉·唐纳利 (Stella Donnelly)、史派西·简 (Spacey Jane) 等人倾力打造一张阳光明媚但奇怪的翻唱专辑</a></strong></li></ul><p>“扭动起来，头晕目眩！”该专辑将于 3 月 7 日发行，届时帕顿和佩克将与其他乡村艺术家一起亮相，如 Dasha、Lainey Wilson、Jackson Dean、MacKenzie Porter 和 Lucky Oceans。</p><p>在其他地方，摩根·埃文斯 (Morgan Evans)、沃尔夫兄弟 (The Wolfe Brothers) 和已故的斯利姆·达斯蒂 (Slim Dusty) 等澳大利亚和新西兰艺人也将出演。</p><p>在谈到这张专辑时，Blue Wiggle 的安东尼·菲尔德 (Anthony Field) 表示：“这是我们参与过的最激动人心的项目之一，事实上，我以前从未在一张专辑上花费过这么多时间。</p><p> “乡村音乐就是讲故事和联系，”他继续说道。 “将 Wiggles 的乐趣和想象力与这些传奇乡村音乐艺术家的合作结合起来，感觉就像是完美的搭配。”</p><p>看看下面由 Dasha 演唱的专辑主打单曲“Wiggle Up, Giddy Up!”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="摇摆起来，头晕目眩！ 🤠 The Wiggles + Dasha 🎶 适合儿童和家庭的乡村音乐" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PuTaLilnr7Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这并不是 The Wiggles 第一次尝试新的音乐类型。去年五月，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wiggles-top-dance-music-chart-in-australia-with-official-album-of-rave-remixes-3752405">凭借锐舞混音专辑《The Wiggles Soundsystem: Rave of Innocence》登上了澳大利亚舞曲排行榜的榜首</a>。它在排行榜上的排名超过了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sia">Sia</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rufus-du-sol">Rufus du Sol</a>等大牌艺术家的作品。</p><p>与此同时，去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/orville-peck-felt-a-little-naked-after-dropping-his-signature-fringed-face-mask-3781839">佩克公开了他标志性面罩的变化，并表示在去掉面罩标志性的流苏后，他感觉自己赤身裸体</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，12 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-announces-open-casting-call-for-dolly-an-original-musical-3819746">帕顿宣布公开招募一部根据她的生活改编的新音乐剧</a>。</p><p>该剧名为<em>《多莉：一部原创音乐剧</em>》，将讲述这位歌手的生活和职业生涯，并将结合她最热门的歌曲和一些专为该剧编写的新材料。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-and-orville-peck-are-set-to-appear-on-the-wiggles-new-country-album-3828033">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 和奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck) 将出现在 The Wiggles 的新乡村专辑中，</a>该专辑首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ;
